          "category": "background_checks",
          "text": "Missouri child care licensing — The mandated responsibility to report any suspected child abuse or neglect to the Children’s Division.",
          "citation": {
            "source": "Missouri 5 CSR 25-500 Staff/Child Ratios",
            "url": "https://www.sos.mo.gov/adrules/csr/current/5csr/5c25-500.pdf",
